                                                                                <item><title><![CDATA[6 Hidden Firefox Settings for Better Privacy and Fewer Distractions]]></title><link>https://www.howtogeek.com/firefox-config-settings/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Shan Abdul]]></dc:creator><enclosure url="https://static0.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/firefox-logo-with-a-settings-icon-and-a-disabled-switch.jpg" length="2568" type="image/jpeg"/><category><![CDATA[Web]]></category><category><![CDATA[Firefox]]></category><category><![CDATA[web browsers]]></category><category><![CDATA[Mozilla]]></category><category><![CDATA[customization]]></category><description><![CDATA[
                                            Customize Firefox the smart way!
                                        ]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[
