                                                                                                                                    <p>The Linux subsystem on Android is capable of opening up a huge range of possibilities. And the vast majority of them can be unlocked once this tiny, but important, change actually makes it to stable Android.</p>                    ]]></content:encoded><pubDate>Fri, 26 Sep 2025 21:36:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.howtogeek.com/linux-apps-on-android-are-one-step-closer-to-reality/</guid></item>                                                                <item><title><![CDATA[Don't Ignore Your TV's Sharpness Setting]]></title><link>https://www.howtogeek.com/dont-ignore-your-tvs-sharpness-setting/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Sydney Butler]]></dc:creator><enclosure url="https://static0.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/shutterstock_708947794.jpg" length="482" type="image/jpeg"/><category><![CDATA[Audio/Video]]></category><category><![CDATA[TVs]]></category><category><![CDATA[Blu-ray]]></category><category><![CDATA[Video Streaming]]></category><description><![CDATA[
                                            Is your TV's sharpness setting ruining your favorite shows?
                                        ]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[
                                                                                                                                    <p>There are so many different settings on your TV, it's hard to know which ones matter and which have a real effect on your viewing experience. Most are pretty self-explanatory, or you can just mess with the ones that aren't and tell what they do by eye.</p>                    ]]></content:encoded><pubDate>Fri, 26 Sep 2025 20:30:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.howtogeek.com/dont-ignore-your-tvs-sharpness-setting/</guid></item>                                                                <item><title><![CDATA[C7 Corvette Buying Guide: Snag a Supercar Bargain]]></title><link>https://www.howtogeek.com/c7-corvette-buying-guide-snag-a-supercar-bargain/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Tyler Dupont]]></dc:creator><enclosure url="https://static0.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/chevrolet-corvette_c7_stingray-2014-hd-32f4fb211bf4c62a4829b434d82fa1c2e7a0ad88a.jpg" length="259" type="image/jpeg"/><category><![CDATA[Automotive]]></category><category><![CDATA[Sports Cars]]></category><category><![CDATA[Chevrolet]]></category><category><![CDATA[2019 Chevrolet Corvette Stingray Coupe]]></category><description><![CDATA[
